## Authentication

The server supports two authentication modes:

### Client Credentials (Two-Legged OAuth)

For server-to-server integrations. Set `BLACKBOARD_CLIENT_ID` and `BLACKBOARD_CLIENT_SECRET`.

### Pre-obtained Token

For testing or external token management. Set `BLACKBOARD_API_TOKEN` instead of client credentials.

